AJU kab´e t-xik´ te Luke Skywalker X-wing fighter n-chi ok tmojb´an kyib´ tun t-xi b´inchen jun t-xik´ extzen aju´ tal bark n-chi b´et t-xilen twitz tx´otx´ te saqb´aqin ex saqb´aqin.

